  Stable amd64, x86.

  26 Jul 2004; Chris White <chriswhite@gentoo.org> faac-1.24.ebuild:
  Fixes circular blocks on mpeg4ip by removing faad2 deps (faad2 is not required
  as a runtime lib, or a build lib).

